<HEADLINE>
FT  04 OCT 94 / UK Company News: TransTec
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
An article published on September 28 noted that TransTec's shares had traded
at more than 500p in 1992. The contrast drawn with the current price was
misleading because the shares were subdivided 1-for-5 in October 1993.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
